  <brief_title>Effect of Noni Juice on Lipid Peroxidation-derived DNA Adducts in Heavy Smokers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double Blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled Clinical Trial of the Effect of Noni Juice on Lipid Peroxidation-derived DNA Adducts in Current Heavy Smokers</official_title>
