  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to determine if noni juice reduces lipid hydroperoxide (LOOH)
      and malondialdehyde (MDA) derived-DNA adducts, markers of oxidative DNA damage, in peripheral
      blood lymphocytes of cigarette smokers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
